  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (West)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Receive, pick, pack and dispatch goods</li><li>Use Warehouse Management system to track inventory </li><li>Help with housekeeping and stock counts to keep things need and tidy</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Entry level candidates are welcome to apply - training will be provided </li><li>Comfortable handling items up to 10kg </li><li>Fixed shift available - free to choose the shifts that you prefer</li><li>Work 5 days a week (might include weekends) </li></ul><p><strong>Working Hours: </strong></p><ul><li>Day shift, 8am to 6pm / Night shift, 8pm to 6am (fixed shift)</li></ul><p><strong>Contract Period: </strong>Minimum 6 months </p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Cogent/Pandan </p><p>EA License No.: 96C4864</p><p>Reg No.: R26159658 BRANN LEONG CHUN HOE </p>",
